rComments: He has the most boring lecture I have ever experienced in my life. Monotone, coffee won't even keep you awake.
He has a very strong accent, not responsible to his students. You will learn almost nothing from him.
Very nice guy, very helpful, his lectures are boring though. Easy exams, good professor overall

This man's lectures are dead boring; he has no idea how to teach a class. Watch out for his tests and exams, he says they're "tricky", which means his English is poor and the tests are too long to be finished in the allotted time (on the bright side, this leads to an incredibly large curve; may it be ever in your favour).
Poor language skills, cannot even recognize his handwriting. Worst prof I've ever had even if he seems like a good guy.

Friendly + knowledgeable. Lectures may get boring. Exams do not test your knowledge as they should. Some True/False questions in the final do not even make sense. Weekly assignments could be better. Overall, he is a nice guy but not the best professor.
